Little Java Project, which is able to write Chrome Extensions. At the moment you can use the classes
and use it in your project or use the Console Version.

	java de.devsurf.chrome.extensions.ConsoleCrxCreator yourapp.crx yourapp.zip yourapp.pem


If packaging your Extension in your Jave Web App, extend your "web.xml" to send the right Mime Type.

	<mime-mapping>
		<extension>crx</extension>
		<mime-type>application/x-chrome-extension</mime-type>
	</mime-mapping>